msgstr "Please check your invitation. This event is invite-only."

#: app.py:133
msgid "By when should I let you know if I’ll be attending?"
msgstr ""

#: app.py:134
msgid "Please, give us your answer by 30/04/2026."
msgstr ""

#: app.py:137
msgid "How should I let you know if I’ll be attending?"
msgstr ""

#: app.py:138
msgid ""
"In true organised fashion, we’ve prepared a lovely little form in the "
"CONFIRMAR PRESENÇA/RVSP section, for you to fill out with the name(s) of "
"the attending guest(s). "
msgstr ""

#: app.py:141
msgid "Are kids welcome?"
msgstr ""

#: app.py:142
msgid ""
"Children are welcome, but please remember to add their names to the RSVP "
"form so we can include them in our final headcount."
msgstr ""

#: app.py:145
msgid "OMG, I see a deer, may I go pet him?"
msgstr ""

#: app.py:146
msgid ""
"Please, bear in mind that Tapada is a wildlife reserve - while the "
"animals may tolerate human visitors, they remain wild. For their safety "
"and yours, we kindly ask that you do not approach or feed them."
msgstr ""

#: app.py:149
msgid "I have a question that's not answered in the FAQ section..."
msgstr ""

#: app.py:150
msgid ""
"In case you have extra questions, feel free to reach our costumer service"
" by phone at 00351917200606 or 00351961115694 (phone calls, SMS or "
"whatsapp), Mon-Fri from 8 a.m.to 8 p.m."
msgstr ""

